    "body": "It seems like \\mu_g sometimes refers to the amount of gas after deducting the intrinsic cost of the operation, while other times it refers to the amount of gas before that deduction, an issue which has already been discussed in https://github.com/ethereum/yellowpaper/issues/325. This causes the possible interpretation given in this issue. Hence, this issue is probably a duplicate of https://github.com/ethereum/yellowpaper/issues/325.",
